{"tid":381604,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"搞手只求打個和 窮撚勿入","createTime":"2017-08-31T05:41:55.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-31T10:24:48.000Z","uid":48883,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"3f0659b5b17ef4657211d99d4cbbdbc3451831c9","tid":381604,"uid":48883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:41:55.000Z","msg":"是咁的，呢個轉會窗死線日，我唔去浦了。夜晚出貨。 搞過歡送會<br />\n我地book 了2位球員。第一位 山齊士 。<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/lw9xeib0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Flw9xeib0&h=a2368518&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/jebcpvkl\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fjebcpvkl&h=f3a33d14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n28歲 可翼可前峰 有鬥心 唔洗休息 50m<br />\n<br />\n另一位, 半青訓的英格蘭人 張伯倫<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/bi2o8qk1\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fbi2o8qk1&h=2527b43f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/h6quzfvk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fh6quzfvk&h=7474c9d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我中意呢位多d，夠後生 仲要係英格蘭人<br />\n全能中場中 40m左右<br />\n<br />\n搞手會印好多球衣 到時一齊著住歡送球員離開<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男球迷：$1000 位 :<br />\n女球迷：Model , 靚女免費。<br />\n普通女仔：唔俾去。<br />\n<br />\n來吧靚女，識d俾得起$1000去歡送的人吧。 <br />\n<br />\np.s. 呢d歡送無得賺，搞手只求打個和，大家開開心心玩返晚。"},{"pid":"a23ee08f01bfb68c7386bcbafb3eb58c4a577b1d","tid":381604,"uid":48883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"735fd59d78ffeaf22723f3630f7db7a22324c8fc","tid":381604,"uid":38390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:46:53.000Z","msg":"john"},{"pid":"2b6ed36f65f498fa70e5ad2c3ee92df6a4ef04e9","tid":381604,"uid":80832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T05:47: